verbose_text: Indeed, Kindlin-1 shRNA mediated abnormal integrin regulation caused cell behavior defects : Transwell assay revealed that in the absence of EGF, PF-573228 suppressed EGF induced HaCaT cell migration (XREF_FIG, lane 3 vs. lane 2); likewise, Kindlin-1 shRNA attenuated HaCaT cell migration compared to the control shRNA group (XREF_FIG, lane 5 vs. lane 4).
evidence: Kindlin-1 shRNA attenuated HaCaT cell migration
